=== EVENT_ESCAPE_POD ===
# id: 1
# title: Escape Pod
# chinese_title: 逃生舱
# category: DistressSignal
# mode: starmap

An escape pod tumbles through the void, its emergency light blinking red. A single occupant appears to be in cryo-stasis.

* [Rescue the survivor]
  ~ gain_crew_member
  救 (jiù) — rescue
* [Strip the pod for parts]
  ~ gain_scrap(8)
  零件 (língjiàn) — parts
* [Scan the pod from a safe distance]
  ~ gain_credits(5)
  扫描 (sǎomiáo) — scan
